de.rwth.i2.attestor.stateSpaceGeneration

Class ViolationPoints

  • java.lang.Object
    • de.rwth.i2.attestor.stateSpaceGeneration.ViolationPoints

  • public class ViolationPoints
extends Object
    A set of violation points. Violation points are pairs of variables and selectors that indicate a missing selector that has to be obtained through materialization.
    Author:
    Christoph
